00:07:28,492 --> 00:07:30,995
Ayo. Di sini. Tendang.

51
00:07:31,078 --> 00:07:32,079
Ayo. Sebelah sini.

52
00:07:32,163 --> 00:07:33,164
Ayo.

53
00:07:33,664 --> 00:07:34,665
Ayo.

54
00:07:35,708 --> 00:07:37,460
-Kau baik-baik saja.
-Tangkap.

55
00:07:38,627 --> 00:07:39,962
Maaf, Tuan.

56
00:07:45,885 --> 00:07:47,845
-Apa ini?
-Kandung kemih babi.

57
00:07:49,305 --> 00:07:50,639
Apa terjadi sesuatu di sini?

58
