59
00:08:24,798 --> 00:08:25,841
Astaga.

60
00:08:27,968 --> 00:08:29,011
Siapa yang bernama George?

61
00:08:31,514 --> 00:08:32,890
Panggil ayahmu.

62
00:08:34,016 --> 00:08:36,268
Ayah! Pembeli.

63
00:08:36,352 --> 00:08:38,145
Kau saja yang layani.

64
00:08:38,229 --> 00:08:39,939
Kau tahu di mana letak sherbet.

65
00:08:40,022 --> 00:08:42,358
Dia tak mau sherbet. Dia menginginkanmu.

66
00:08:43,192 --> 00:08:44,193
Wanita?

67
00:08:48,072 --> 00:08:49,114
Hai, Ayah.

68
00:08:57,373 --> 00:09:00,417
Roxy. Di mana Roxy? Roxy.

69
00:09:00,501 --> 00:09:02,545
-Nell-mu kembali!
-Apa?

70
00:09:02,628 --> 00:09:04,797
Nell. Nell-mu. Dia kembali.

71
00:09:06,507 --> 00:09:07,675
Nell sudah mati.

72
00:09:13,305 --> 00:09:14,390
Aku janda.

73
00:09:15,349 --> 00:09:17,726
Kapten Jackson, dia tewas. Sudah mati.

74
00:09:18,310 --> 00:09:20,521
Dia terbelah dua di Pertempuran Blenheim.

75
00:09:21,814 --> 00:09:22,856
Dan kau bersamanya.

76
00:09:24,108 --> 00:09:25,109
Itu yang kami dengar.

77
00:09:27,945 --> 00:09:30,364
Ternyata itu sebabnya semua orang
menatapku aneh.

78
00:09:33,367 --> 00:09:39,415
Jadi, apa aku bisa menginap di sini
beberapa malam?

79
00:09:39,498 --> 00:09:42,918
Kukira kau tak mau berurusan
dengan kami, kaum lemah.

80
00:09:44,420 --> 00:09:45,713
Itu kata-kata terakhir
yang keluar dari mulutmu

81
